    <span class="author" data-post-author="Jeremy2013"><a href="http://arstechnica.com/civis/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=397705&amp;sid=f0c298d4d33b37fc59279c7b706622ca">Jeremy2013</a></span><span class="rank">Ars Scholae Palatinae</span>
