he insane, Snowden went to the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fourth_branch_of_government" class="postlink" rel="nofollow">Fourth Branch of Government</a>. <br /><br />It is vital to understanding the context to see Snowden as one of many attempts at fixing the US intelligence community rather than a single isolated event. He didn't go to the public as a first resort, he did it because multiple people in his position had already tried the first resort and been utterly punished for it.
      
